        ": سمعت أبا عبدالله عليه السلام يقول: إن القرآن زاجر وآمر يأمر بالجنة ويزجر عن النار"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "[2/1542] al-Kafi: Humayd b. Ziyad from al-Hasan b. Muhammad from Wuhayb b. Hafs from Abi Basir who said: I heard Aba Abdillah عليه السلام saying: The Qur’an is a Chaser and a Caller. It calls to the Garden and chases away from the Fire"
        ]
      }
